{"lemma":"أَسام","slug":"أَسام","root":"س.م.#","root_slug":"س-م-_","root_link":"/words/roots/س-م-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ٱِسْم","root":"سمو","pos":"N","occurrence_count":39},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n783","n20831","n20616"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%85"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n783","headword_ar":"اِسْمٌ","root":"Asm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"smw","text_ar":"سمو"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n20831","headword_ar":"اِسْمٌ","root":"smw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) with the conjunctive"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":", [i. e. written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@somN","text_ar":"ا@سْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] but this is made disjunctive by poetic license [as well as when the word commences a sentence], (S,) usually with kesr [when the | is disjunctive], (Lh, M, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AusomN","text_ar":"اُسْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) of the dial. of Benoo-'Amr-Ibn-Temeem and of Kudá'ah, (M, TA,) mentioned by IAar, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"simN","text_ar":"سِمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sumN","text_ar":"سُمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samN","text_ar":"سَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sumFA","text_ar":"سُمًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"simFA","text_ar":"سِمًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samFA","text_ar":"سَمًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"name"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing; i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sign"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as may be uttered or written"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conveying knowledge"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaAmapN","text_ar":"عَلَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a word applied to denote a substance"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an accident"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attribute, for the purpose of distinction:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a substantive in the proper sense of this term,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a real substantive;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a substance in a tropical sense of this term,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an ideal substantive:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as expl. by El-Munáwee, in the “ Towkeef, ” the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Asm","text_ar":"اسم"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which denotes a meaning in itself unconnected with any of the three times"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"past and present and future"},{"kind":"text","text":"]:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"if denoting what subsists by itself, it is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisomu EayonK","text_ar":"اِسْمُ عَيْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"if denoting what does not subsist by itself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an accident"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attribute,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether existent, as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEilomu","text_ar":"العِلْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knowledge"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"or non-existent, as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljaholu","text_ar":"الجَهْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignorance"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisomu maEonFY","text_ar":"اِسْمُ مَعْنًى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asomaA='N","text_ar":"اَسْمَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of pauc.] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asomaAwaAtN","text_ar":"اَسْمَاوَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) the latter said by Lh to be a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisomN","text_ar":"اِسْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but it is rather a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asomaA='N","text_ar":"اَسْمَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for otherwise there is no way of accounting for it, (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asaAmK","text_ar":"اَسَامٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asaAmiY~u","text_ar":"اَسَامِىُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) are [likewise] pls. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asomaA='N","text_ar":"اَسْمَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, * TA:) the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@somN","text_ar":"ا@سْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisomN","text_ar":"اِسْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AusomN","text_ar":"اُسْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is derived from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samawotu","text_ar":"سَمَوْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) or from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~umuw~u","text_ar":"السُّمُوُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, Er-Rághib, TA,) because the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Asm","text_ar":"اسم"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a means of raising into notice the thing denoted thereby, and making it known: (S, * Er-Rághib, TA:) it is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifoEN","text_ar":"اِفْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AufoEN","text_ar":"اُفْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to different dialects], the last radical,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":", being wanting in it, (S, Msb, TA,) and the hemzeh [or rather |] being prefixed by way of compensation for it, accord to a general rule; (Msb, TA;) for it is originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"simowN","text_ar":"سِمْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, Er-Rághib, TA) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sumowN","text_ar":"سُمْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, TA,) its pl. being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asomaA='N","text_ar":"اَسْمَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and its dim. being ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sumaY~N","text_ar":"سُمَىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samayowN","text_ar":"سَمَيْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, Msb, Er-Rághib, * TA:) some of the Koofees hold that it is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwasomu","text_ar":"الوَسْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEalaAmapu","text_ar":"العَلَامَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the primal radical, being rejected, and the hemzeh [or |] being substituted for it, so that its measure is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiEolN","text_ar":"اِعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AuEolN","text_ar":"اُعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; but this is a weak opinion, for, were it so, the dim. would be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wasayomN","text_ar":"وَسَيْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the pl. would be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awosaAmN","text_ar":"اَوْسَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisomu h`*aA ka*aA","text_ar":"اِسْمُ هٰذَا كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The name of this is thus,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a word"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and if you will you may say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ausomu h`*A k*A","text_ar":"اُسْمُ هٰذا كذا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and in like manner, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"simuhu","text_ar":"سِمُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sumuhu","text_ar":"سُمُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": Lh says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisomuhu fulaAnN","text_ar":"اِسْمُهُ فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His name is Such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is the [common] phrase of the Arabs; and he mentions"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ausomuhu fulaAnN","text_ar":"اُسْمُهُ فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as heard from [the tribe of] Benoo-'Amr-Ibn-Temeem: and Ks cites, as heard from some of [the tribe of] Benoo-Kudá'ah, the saying,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"↓ \n      biA@somi A@l~a*iY fiY kul~i suwrapK sumuho"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the name of Him whose name is in every chapter of the Kur-án"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"simuho","text_ar":"سِمُهْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"as heard from others, not of Kudá'ah. (M.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siro EalaY A@somi A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"سِرْ عَلَى ا@سْمِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an elliptical phrase [for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siro muEotamidFA EalaY *ikori A@somi","text_ar":"سِرْ مُعْتَمِدًا عَلَى ذِكْرِ ا@سْمِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Journey thou relying upon the mention of the name of God"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IJ, M in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dl","text_ar":"دل"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daliylN","text_ar":"دَلِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@somN","text_ar":"ا@سْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fame, renown, report,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reputation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a person: (TA:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sumFA","text_ar":"سُمًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in relation to good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) not to evil; mentioned by Az. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahaba A@somuhu","text_ar":"ذَهَبَ ا@سْمُهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"فِى النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His fame"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spread, among mankind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the people"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","Lh","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n20616","headword_ar":"اَسَمُّ","root":"sm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A nose"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and fat"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the nostrils."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]}]}}